cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a framework for optimization, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of batch optimization and the comparison to stochastic approaches suggest that the paper may belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus on efficiency and resource constraints may also suggest a connection to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the use of optimization techniques may also suggest a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV).
